"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3><a href="fiction: %E2%80%98The Brothers Karamazov%E2%80%99" class="icon none"></a> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-the-brothers-karamazov-4776b0b1?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">小说：《卡拉马佐夫兄弟》</a> </h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-the-brothers-karamazov-4776b0b1"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-829534?width=700&amp;height=503" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">布里奇曼图片</span></div></div></div><p>在新译本中，陀思妥耶夫斯基的巨著成为了世界末日精神危机的独特写照。<em>萨克斯评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-the-brothers-karamazov-4776b0b1?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/august-wilson-review-staging-the-blues-d28ffa2a?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《奥古斯特·威尔逊》评论：上演布鲁斯</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/august-wilson-review-staging-the-blues-d28ffa2a"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-829333?width=700&amp;height=475" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">汤姆·斯威尼/明尼阿波利斯明星论坛报/ZUMA/Alamy</span></div></div></div><p>这位剧作家对黑人生活和历史的胜利而令人心碎的描述超越了流派，改变了美国戏剧。<em>艾萨克·巴特勒评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/august-wilson-review-staging-the-blues-d28ffa2a?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/science-fiction-fantasy-tolkien-forever-6965044d?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">科幻与奇幻：永远的托尔金</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
