"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/science-fiction-fantasy-tolkien-forever-6965044d"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-828178?width=700&amp;height=403" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit"></span></div></div></div><p>对《二十一世纪的托尔金》、《霍比特人的历史》和托尔金自己的《马尔登之战》的评论。<em>莉兹·布拉斯韦尔的评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/science-fiction-fantasy-tolkien-forever-6965044d?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/two-books-on-peter-beard-cfc2a4ac?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">两本关于彼得·比尔德的书</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/two-books-on-peter-beard-cfc2a4ac"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-829073?width=700&amp;height=464" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">哈坎·路德维格森</span></div></div></div><p>在工作中，这位野生动物摄影师曾被大象顶伤。在下班时间，他因热衷于派对和宣传而声名狼藉。<em>多米尼克·格林评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/two-books-on-peter-beard-cfc2a4ac?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/five-best-books-on-libraries-2b506037?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">五本最佳图书馆书籍</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/five-best-books-on-libraries-2b506037"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-829301?width=700&amp;height=466" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
